                    <span>I used this book when I was job searching during my senior year of  college.  I read it cover to cover, and followed the author's advice.  I  was highly successful in my job search, landing my dream job.  I was even  complimented several times on my "very creative" cover letter.   You can't go wrong with this book!</span>
                  
